Take off that shirt

153
00:14:50,522 --> 00:14:53,013
l'm sorry, l don't believe
beauty needs cheap exposure

154
00:14:53,225 --> 00:14:55,352
One tight slap
and all your beliefs will change

155
00:14:55,661 --> 00:14:57,856
