a list like this one

234
00:21:45,337 --> 00:21:47,430
Talk of investments

235
00:21:48,607 --> 00:21:53,840
Small town-guys have a habit of
dreaming big. No ban on dreaming

236
00:21:54,046 --> 00:21:54,512
lndulge yourself

237
00:21:54,713 --> 00:21:58,342
But next time,
come up with a scheme that...

238
00:21:58,550 --> 00:22:03,749
a thousand others haven't thought up
before you. Get it ? Now excuse me

239
00:22:16,902 --> 00:22:19,166
Where are you going, lady?
- To enter the contest

240
00:22:19,371 --> 00:22:21,635
You can't go in.
- lf l can't go inside...

241
00:22:21,840 --> 00:22:25,241
how do l take part in the competition?
Let me in. l've come really far

242
00:22:25,444 --> 00:22:28,777
l said, you can't go in.
- l say, l have to enter

243
00:22:34,553 --> 00:22:36,953
Can l help you ?
- Yes, myself Vimmi Saluja...

244
00:22:37,155 --> 00:22:39,180
l've come to enter the contest.
- You're too late

245
00:22:39,391 --> 00:22:42,588
What...?
- The entries closed two days ago

246
00:22:42,828 --> 00:22:44,625
You mean the contest's begun?
- No, not yet

247
00:22:44,830 --> 00:22:47,424
Oh, that's a relief.
- l said, entries have closed

248
00:22:47,632 --> 00:22:51,398
But the contest hasn't begun!
- l said ''the-entries-have-closed''

249
00:22:51,603 --> 00:22:53,400
So open up for two minutes,
l'll quickly squeeze in !

250
00:22:53,605 --> 00:22:56,472
You're from some village?
Miss Quickly-squeeze-in !

251
00:22:56,675 --> 00:23:00,236
This is no village fair
to squeeze-in-slip-out when-you-wish

252
00:23:00,445 --> 00:23:03,676
This is the Miss lndia contest,
but what would you know ?

253
00:23:04,349 --> 00:23:05,816
Oh c'mon Pammi, forget it

254
00:23:06,017 --> 00:23:10,477
One minute... would l know what ?
- The desire and the ability...

255
00:23:10,689 --> 00:23:13,886
to become Miss lndia are two very
different things. So go home...

256
00:23:14,092 --> 00:23:17,653
and start a beauty parlour.
- Why not beauty-parlour yourself ?

257
00:23:17,863 --> 00:23:18,488
Excuse me ?

258
00:23:18,697 --> 00:23:21,689
Ever watched your figure ?
At least ten kilos overweight...

259
00:23:21,900 --> 00:23:24,494
with black-dyed hair and
desperately-curving-lipline...

260
00:23:24,703 --> 00:23:29,504
with miles-thick lipstick. You know all
about make-up. Beauty parlour's for you

261
00:23:29,708 --> 00:23:30,766
What a bitch

262
00:24:00,205 --> 00:24:01,001
Listen...

263
00:24:03,408 --> 00:24:06,809
Yes?
- Please come with me to the toilet

264
00:24:07,813 --> 00:24:12,477
lt's right at the end of the platform
and it's really dark

265
00:24:17,489 --> 00:24:18,251
Come

266
00:24:24,729 --> 00:24:27,493
Weren't you on the
Jhansi Mail this morning ?

267
00:24:29,234 --> 00:24:36,265
Returning? Here on business?
- Yes l came for the Miss lndia contest

268
00:24:40,912 --> 00:24:41,970
So how was it ?

269
00:24:43,982 --> 00:24:46,450
Good... very good

270
00:24:47,452 --> 00:24:50,444
l got through the first round

271
00:24:51,523 --> 00:24:54,117
Good... good... Miss lndia !

272
00:24:55,861 --> 00:25:00,298
And you ? Here on business too?
- Oh no... no...

273
00:25:02,767 --> 00:25:04,428
Work is something
l don't really believe in

274
00:25:05,170 --> 00:25:06,933
l came here for a meeting

275
00:25:07,706 --> 00:25:12,336
There's a finance company here,
they want to buy my scheme

276
00:25:14,112 --> 00:25:17,946
l had to come personally you see,
it's a matter of millions

277
00:25:19,551 --> 00:25:25,615
So, you're becoming
a model soon?- l guess so

278
00:25:26,992 --> 00:25:32,020
You'll become famous.
- Yes... l guess so

279
00:25:33,164 --> 00:25:35,359
People will buzz around you
like bees around honey

280
00:25:35,834 --> 00:25:38,826
Yes... l guess they will

281
00:25:44,142 --> 00:25:47,373
Why are you crying ?

282
00:25:47,679 --> 00:25:51,046
l didn't mean to insult you

283
00:25:53,585 --> 00:25:55,382
No, don't take me otherwise

284
00:25:55,587 --> 00:25:59,284
l belong to a decent family,
l wouldn't dream of it

285
00:25:59,791 --> 00:26:03,056
Calm down, everyone's watching

286
00:26:03,261 --> 00:26:06,230
Poor thing... she's in grieving

287
00:26:06,431 --> 00:26:08,331
l was only sympathising...

288
00:26:11,469 --> 00:26:12,800
Everything's fine

289
00:26:19,377 --> 00:26:22,244
You'll be the first girl to cry after
making it to the Miss lndia contest

290
00:26:28,954 --> 00:26:32,651
l didn't make it anywhere

291
00:26:35,727 --> 00:26:37,285
Aren't you ashamed of lying ?

292
00:26:44,402 --> 00:26:46,996
Actually, l lied too...

293
00:26:47,806 --> 00:26:50,639
the manager of the finance company
didn't quite buy my scheme...

294
00:26:50,842 --> 00:26:52,707
l think he doesn't have the drive

295
00:26:54,980 --> 00:26:55,844
Bloody idiot

296
00:26:56,481 --> 00:27:00,281
Foulmouthing... me...?

297
00:27:00,986 --> 00:27:02,681
Escort her to the loo
and then get abused for it ?

298
00:27:03,655 --> 00:27:06,783
l escorted you !
Who do you think you are ?

299
00:27:14,165 --> 00:27:19,000
You mean if you go back now...?
- Wedding bells...

300
00:27:20,338 --> 00:27:23,330
That's too bad. - Very

301
00:27:23,842 --> 00:27:24,399
Then ?

302
00:27:29,047 --> 00:27:36,317
l'll run away.
- You already have

303
00:27:38,289 --> 00:27:43,693
So, what'll you do now?
- What'll you do ?

304
00:27:46,531 --> 00:27:50,058
Whatever l do, l'm not giving up.
And l'm not going back home

305
00:27:50,268 --> 00:27:56,434
Then, where will you go? - Kanpur

306
00:27:57,275 --> 00:28:01,143
Why Kanpur?
- The company has a head office there

307
00:28:01,346 --> 00:28:05,305
l'll show my scheme to senior officers,
l'm sure they'll get it

308
00:28:07,619 --> 00:28:10,383
Why don't you come
along to Kanpur? - Who me...?

309
00:28:12,123 --> 00:28:15,650
Miss lndia contests are held all over.
Maybe they'll allow you to enter there

310
00:28:17,162 --> 00:28:21,496
You got to find a way into the contest,
else what use was running away ?

311
00:28:45,056 --> 00:28:48,924
So long, l guess the next time
l see you it'll be on TV

312
00:28:49,327 --> 00:28:55,266
l guess so. Thank you.
And good luck for your big meeting

313
00:28:56,101 --> 00:29:00,663
Thanks but that was superfluous. l only
need to make a presentation and...

314
00:29:00,872 --> 00:29:02,999
voila ! l'll have 1 00 finance companies
running rings around me

315
00:29:05,443 --> 00:29:07,968
See you

316
00:29:10,815 --> 00:29:17,379
Unbelievable. Got to admit...
very few people have brains as sharp

317
00:29:18,089 --> 00:29:25,962
l say, just once in a whole year,
let me meet just one such person

318
00:29:27,565 --> 00:29:35,370
But two in a single day, unbelievable!
Would you believe...

319
00:29:36,007 --> 00:29:40,103
just half an hour ago, another man
came to me with an identical scheme

320
00:29:41,913 --> 00:29:45,815
Who?
- Manager of our Lucknow branch...

321
00:29:46,017 --> 00:29:51,250
Mr Qureishi ! lmagine... a rare gem
lay buried in my own backyard

322
00:29:52,423 --> 00:30:01,092
He got a 1 0,000 bonus on the spot !
He even had a list of 500 investors

323
00:30:01,432 --> 00:30:03,832
Unbelievable ! What a man !
- Where's he staying ?

324
00:30:04,035 --> 00:30:08,995
Landmark Hotel.
- ln Landmark ! And why not ?

325
00:30:09,207 --> 00:30:17,740
The 1 0,000 bonus ! Give me as much
l'll go to live in a five star too

326
00:30:18,516 --> 00:30:20,643
Next?- Vimmi Saluja

327
00:30:20,852 --> 00:30:23,821
Address?
- 2/5 Ballygunj, Pankinagar

328
00:30:28,626 --> 00:30:29,854
One minute...

329
00:30:32,297 --> 00:30:36,427
Doesn't Pankinagar fall within
the Lucknow district ?

330
00:30:37,202 --> 00:30:39,363
lt does?
- Yes, Lucknow district

331
00:30:40,405 --> 00:30:46,071
You didn't fill up the form in Lucknow?
- What difference, here or there ?

332
00:30:46,277 --> 00:30:48,837
l was passing through Kanpur
so l thought l'll get it over with

333
00:30:49,514 --> 00:30:50,105
Very good

334
00:30:51,149 --> 00:30:52,810
Please step outside

335
00:30:53,685 --> 00:30:59,487
Sir'ji, just a matter of an address...
- Go away ! Rules are rules

336
00:30:59,724 --> 00:31:01,191
Please...- Get lost

337
00:31:02,360 --> 00:31:04,021
Oversmartness

338
00:31:12,270 --> 00:31:16,764
Look, l can't bend the rules

339
00:31:17,475 --> 00:31:21,138
But if you wish...

340
00:31:22,146 --> 00:31:23,511
l can forget rules for a while

341
00:31:24,582 --> 00:31:28,780
Yes sir!
- But nothing comes for free

342
00:31:29,153 --> 00:31:32,054
Sir, l'll do whatever you wish !

343
00:31:32,257 --> 00:31:36,091
Very good!
Once you're Miss lndia...

344
00:31:36,294 --> 00:31:42,062
you'll have all the wealth,
all the fame your heart ever desired

345
00:31:43,401 --> 00:31:47,804
But l? l'm still stuck to the same
... chair and table

346
00:31:48,273 --> 00:31:48,864
Oh sure...

347
00:31:49,173 --> 00:31:56,511
l have nothing right now...
but l promise, when l'm Miss lndia...

348
00:31:56,714 --> 00:32:00,377
l'll pay you...
everything you'll ever want

349
00:32:01,452 --> 00:32:08,255
You're mistaken. You have everything
l'll ever want... right now

350
00:32:09,027 --> 00:32:17,025
l won't force you. Registration closes
in five minutes. Think it over

351
00:32:17,502 --> 00:32:19,902
You'll find me at the same table

352
00:33:00,378 --> 00:33:01,845
What's your name?- Jajjan

353
00:33:03,181 --> 00:33:05,240
You make tea?
- No, l serve tea

354
00:33:11,889 --> 00:33:15,120
This world we live in boy,
has two kinds of people

355
00:33:15,626 --> 00:33:19,687
One, those who serve tea.
And those to whom tea is served

356
00:33:20,331 --> 00:33:23,562
The faster you become one of the latter,
the better the life that you'll live

357
00:33:24,268 --> 00:33:25,496
Has somebody hurt you ?

358
00:33:34,278 --> 00:33:35,472
Two teas and chips

359
00:33:36,647 --> 00:33:37,511
Two?

360
00:33:38,249 --> 00:33:41,946
Why ? Problem ?
- No. But who's the second cup for?

361
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:45,052
lf l drink two cups,
will it start a war?

362
00:33:46,057 --> 00:33:49,515
God, this world we live in...!
Get a hold on this kid

363
00:33:52,663 --> 00:33:54,893
lt's no use. - What ?

364
00:33:56,334 --> 00:34:00,668
No use being earnest, unwitting fools
getting shoved in stinking little towns

365
00:34:01,105 --> 00:34:04,040
Then...?- Bombay...

366
00:34:05,877 --> 00:34:09,108
the only city in all of lndia where
a man is recognised for his worth...

367
00:34:10,515 --> 00:34:15,714
the only place where you can start from
the pavement and end up in palaces...

368
00:34:15,920 --> 00:34:18,889
where ambition isn't pushed around,
but cheered, egging you on

369
00:34:19,624 --> 00:34:21,148
How're you so sure?
- How...

370
00:34:22,427 --> 00:34:26,295
if Dhirubhai Ambani, Ratan Tata, Birla
had been in Lucknow-Kanpur...

371
00:34:26,497 --> 00:34:28,795
they'd be swatting flies in
Ambani General Stores, Tata Flour Mills

372
00:34:29,000 --> 00:34:34,097
And Birla Tobacco Stall. Bombay...
gave them the recognition they deserved

373
00:34:34,372 --> 00:34:35,634
Look where it got them...

374
00:34:38,242 --> 00:34:40,506
So you want to go Bombay ?

375
00:34:42,914 --> 00:34:45,382
You can come along too.
What'll you do here ?

376
00:34:46,717 --> 00:34:51,313
All the top models are in Bombay. Damn
this narrow-minded small-town mob

377
00:34:52,523 --> 00:34:55,583
lt's the place for Miss lndia, no?- Yes

378
00:34:58,129 --> 00:35:01,621
A ticket to Bombay,
how much would it cost ?

379
00:35:03,534 --> 00:35:05,001
Not that l have that kind of cash

380
00:35:12,276 --> 00:35:14,801
l got the cash, don't worry.
- What...?

381
00:35:15,079 --> 00:35:20,016
We've seen where truth has landed us.
Now let's say what they want to hear

382
00:35:20,418 --> 00:35:23,979
And what's that...?
- Oi Jajjan, where's Landmark Hotel ?

383
00:35:26,424 --> 00:35:28,153
One whiskey...
- Which one sir ?

384
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:31,851
lmported. How much for a Black Label?
- Four hundred, sir

385
00:35:32,063 --> 00:35:33,826
For a bottle ?- No. 30 ml

386
00:35:34,198 --> 00:35:34,892
Small peg

387
00:35:35,500 --> 00:35:40,267
l'll try an lndian whiskey for a change.
And don't forget the peanuts

388
00:35:44,609 --> 00:35:47,203
Some pretty suave people
you got walking into this Gazal Bar

389
00:35:53,451 --> 00:35:54,383
One Black Label

390
00:35:54,585 --> 00:35:55,176
Sir

391
00:35:58,656 --> 00:36:01,181
Sir ! You here ?

392
00:36:01,559 --> 00:36:05,256
Fursatganj ! All of Lucknow seems to be
pouring into Kanpur today

393
00:36:05,463 --> 00:36:08,955
Slick ! What are you doing here ?
- You'll be seeing more of me here

394
00:36:09,400 --> 00:36:13,063
What do you mean ?
- My scheme got rocking

395
00:36:13,271 --> 00:36:16,672
Which... the same one ?
- No... it was unworkable

396
00:36:16,874 --> 00:36:20,469
You tipped me off in time.
l could've wasted another good year

397
00:36:21,012 --> 00:36:24,914
This is another scheme.
- Which is this ?

398
00:36:25,349 --> 00:36:31,185
l explained this scheme, they offered me
a two per cent stake in the channel

399
00:36:32,256 --> 00:36:34,622
What channel...?
- A news channel

400
00:36:35,693 --> 00:36:36,785
News channel

401
00:36:38,396 --> 00:36:43,925
Nowadays this news channel business
is taking off like a rocket

402
00:36:44,335 --> 00:36:48,999
ln 3 months, they're giving investors
a 300 per cent return on investment

403
00:36:49,207 --> 00:36:51,937
Cigarette ? - Really ?

404
00:36:52,176 --> 00:36:56,078
How much... is the investment ?
- At least 1 00,000

405
00:36:58,449 --> 00:37:02,408
Won't they take a little less ?
l mean, l could invest too...?

406
00:37:02,620 --> 00:37:04,884
Why don't you have a chat ?

407
00:37:09,727 --> 00:37:10,785
Give me an introduction

408
00:37:17,735 --> 00:37:21,193
This is Mr Qureishi
- Q.Q.Qureishi

409
00:37:22,106 --> 00:37:30,411
Q.Q.Qureishi, a very dear friend.
Whatever l am today is because of him

410
00:37:39,957 --> 00:37:44,053
Mr Qureishi would like to invest
in the channel

411
00:37:44,662 --> 00:37:46,152
How many millions ?

412
00:37:47,098 --> 00:37:51,797
He's not like other investors...
this is just a friendly gesture...

413
00:37:52,003 --> 00:37:53,402
about ten thousand ?- Ten

414
00:37:54,705 --> 00:37:55,467
Ten...?

415
00:37:57,008 --> 00:37:57,667
Fifteen... ?

416
00:37:59,777 --> 00:38:02,803
But you're aware,
it should be at least...

417
00:38:04,649 --> 00:38:07,743
Ok, all right,
now how can l refuse you ?

418
00:38:11,656 --> 00:38:18,084
One request, this remains between us
... let this be our little secret

419
00:38:19,263 --> 00:38:22,096
No, no... !
- Promise

420
00:38:24,368 --> 00:38:26,700
We must be in Delhi by morning

421
00:38:29,707 --> 00:38:31,072
So you take the cash from him...

422
00:38:31,842 --> 00:38:33,742
and fetch us a receipt from my room

423
00:38:34,545 --> 00:38:39,039
ln the meantime, if he has no objections
Mr Qureishi can give me company

424
00:38:40,351 --> 00:38:40,908
Yes ?

425
00:38:43,054 --> 00:38:45,750
Well ?- No... l mean no problem

426
00:38:52,296 --> 00:38:52,853
Ten ?

427
00:38:58,035 --> 00:38:59,832
Fursatganj, don't forget the receipt

428
00:39:06,777 --> 00:39:14,684
Would you like to
dance with me Mr Q.Q.Qureishi ?

429
00:39:23,594 --> 00:39:26,222
You dance really well.- Thank you

430
00:39:29,300 --> 00:39:31,666
Where's the ladies' room ?
- Thank you

431
00:39:32,403 --> 00:39:37,102
The washroom... where is it ?
- Bartender, where's the washroom ?

432
00:39:49,754 --> 00:39:51,119
Run

433
00:40:04,201 --> 00:40:05,998
What d'you think of my acting ?
Better than yours ?

434
00:40:08,072 --> 00:40:11,405
Who conned him to your table ?
- Who made the sucker dance ?

435
00:40:18,382 --> 00:40:20,646
l'd love to see Q.Q.Qureishi dancing

436
00:40:24,488 --> 00:40:26,956
Hey, the cash

437
00:40:27,725 --> 00:40:28,419
Some sample

438
00:40:31,562 --> 00:40:33,860
Your share. - You keep it

439
00:40:34,532 --> 00:40:37,160
lt's your share.- Not a gift

440
00:40:37,401 --> 00:40:40,768
Just bank it for me till Bombay.
l can't manage money

441
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:45,100
We had fun though, no ?

442
00:40:49,180 --> 00:40:49,942
Lots...

443
00:41:06,263 --> 00:41:07,821
Move it. Sit in the bus

444
00:41:08,032 --> 00:41:13,561
Passengers for Dehradun and Ambala,
your bus is leaving

445
00:41:16,507 --> 00:41:17,599
Name ?- Bunty

446
00:41:19,610 --> 00:41:20,406
And the Mrs ?

447
00:41:21,879 --> 00:41:22,436
Babli

448
00:41:23,214 --> 00:41:27,241
Bunty... Babli... seats 2 1 and 22

449
00:41:28,252 --> 00:41:29,116
Get inside

450
00:41:33,858 --> 00:41:38,955
Bunty... Babli... what the hell...?
- Nothing... move on. 2 1 and 22

451
00:41:41,398 --> 00:41:44,299
What do you mean nothing?
- Sit down, l'll explain

452
00:41:45,102 --> 00:41:50,005
When l was a kid l always blamed
Bunty for all the mischief l did

453
00:41:50,741 --> 00:41:53,835
And we've just stolen money. So...
- But... what the hell is Babli ?

454
00:41:54,311 --> 00:41:56,973
Why, what's wrong ?
l don't have a problem with Bunty

455
00:41:57,248 --> 00:42:01,082
You look like your Bunty !
But Babli... she sounds like a fat slob

456
00:42:02,219 --> 00:42:06,656
Fat or thin, now it's sealed.
- You could've asked me

457
00:42:07,591 --> 00:42:09,559
Ask my wife her name
in front of a bus conductor ?

458
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:14,459
Who are you calling your wife ?
- l didn't say that, he thought so

459
00:42:14,665 --> 00:42:20,297
And you let it pass ! Now everyone
in this bus thinks l'm Bunty's wife

460
00:42:23,941 --> 00:42:27,877
What are you doing ? Everyone will
think Bunty's wife is a shrew

461
00:42:28,312 --> 00:42:30,872
Stop it !
- You stop it

462
00:42:32,216 --> 00:42:34,309
l'm not talking.- Suits me

463
00:42:34,518 --> 00:42:35,348
Babli, big deal

464
00:42:58,776 --> 00:43:02,735
At least we managed enough
to get us to Bombay

465
00:43:06,116 --> 00:43:08,744
This stash won't last us
a week in Bombay

466
00:43:09,620 --> 00:43:10,450
And...?

467
00:43:12,356 --> 00:43:19,421
And... l think we'll need lots more
if we want to make it in Bombay

468
00:43:20,798 --> 00:43:23,562
Where will we get so much money ?
- The same place we got this from

469
00:43:24,134 --> 00:43:25,123
You mean another... ?

470
00:43:25,803 --> 00:43:32,606
