do you want to go to son ?

1336
02:16:45,756 --> 02:16:48,452
The biggest...
the biggest hospital in Delhi

1337
02:16:48,659 --> 02:16:53,062
Not a hospital or nursing home,
they'll go to a nondescript clinic

