growing up behind bars...

1390
02:23:31,895 --> 02:23:33,590
or dying young on the run

1391
02:23:35,065 --> 02:23:40,435
Do you remember agreeing on
all our marriage vows except...

1392
02:23:40,838 --> 02:23:42,533
We'll be Bunty-Babli
for the rest of our lives

1393
02:23:42,840 --> 02:23:46,537
And we'll live out all our dreams.
- Except...

1394
02:23:47,578 --> 02:23:50,547
Except...?
- Leave that to me

1395
02:23:51,582 --> 02:23:52,207
Okay

1396
02:23:52,983 --> 02:23:54,382
This is the exception Rakesh

1397
02:23:55,586 --> 02:23:58,487
You're getting over-emotional
