1410
02:25:24,007 --> 02:25:26,567
Oye Rakesh, you're in love

1411
02:25:28,679 --> 02:25:30,306
Oh all right

1412
02:25:33,183 --> 02:25:39,315
Rakesh my boy, this world we live in
has two kinds of men. One...

1413
02:25:39,523 --> 02:25:41,320
the kind that thinks twice
before getting married

1414
02:25:41,525 --> 02:25:44,494
And the kind that thinks afterwards
like you, you idiot

1415
02:25:49,199 --> 02:25:50,496
Two tickets for Fursatganj

1416
02:25:50,868 --> 02:25:51,459
Name ?

1417
02:25:52,536 --> 02:25:54,163
Rakesh Trivedi, Vimmi Trivedi

1418
02:25:57,708 --> 02:25:59,175
Bunty and Babli

