You must be tired

1420
02:26:40,918 --> 02:26:42,044
Can we have some water ?

1421
02:26:44,254 --> 02:26:45,221
Die of thirst dog !

1422
02:26:46,590 --> 02:26:48,114
Not for me. For the two of them

1423
02:27:11,114 --> 02:27:15,414
You won't believe me but we quit
being crooks half an hour ago

1424
02:27:17,788 --> 02:27:23,249
Absolutely right, l won't believe you.
- But if l insist l'm telling the truth ?

1425
02:27:23,460 --> 02:27:27,089
l'll start doing right now
what l had planned to do to you in jail

1426
02:27:29,633 --> 02:27:32,431
Why are you looking at me like that ?
- He's telling the truth

1427
02:27:32,970 --> 02:27:36,428
Guaranteed by you,
lndia's biggest bonafide liar ?

1428
02:27:37,808 --> 02:27:39,105
l'm not lying

1429
02:27:39,409 --> 02:27:42,606
A dog's tail insists it became
ramrod straight half an hour ago ?

1430
02:27:42,813 --> 02:27:47,716
You're as old as my father... no one's
had the cheek to talk to her like that

1431
02:27:48,318 --> 02:27:51,287
So you respect your elders now, do you ?
- And why shouldn't we ?

1432
02:27:51,488 --> 02:27:53,786
Now don't tell me you pray
first thing every morning too !

1433
02:27:53,991 --> 02:27:54,958
She does

1434
02:27:55,659 --> 02:27:57,627
So...?
- So what !

1435
02:27:58,095 --> 02:28:03,465
Now you pray to your heart's content
in jail ! lt's all your fault...

1436
02:28:03,667 --> 02:28:05,464
now suffer.
- My fault ?

1437
02:28:06,003 --> 02:28:09,063
Who's idea was it to go straight ?
- lt was for a good cause...

1438
02:28:09,273 --> 02:28:12,071
do you want your son to go to jail ?
- So where's he going now ?

1439
02:28:12,442 --> 02:28:18,642
Now l see how the two of you
have been fooling people for years

1440
02:28:22,352 --> 02:28:23,478
Pappu is hungry

1441
02:28:24,855 --> 02:28:27,983
Pappu ?
When did we start calling him Pappu ?

1442
02:28:28,191 --> 02:28:32,560
Got to call him something no?
You're thinking of the gold all the time

1443
02:28:35,832 --> 02:28:41,361
Let's step outside for a while

1444
02:28:42,873 --> 02:28:45,341
l'm not going anywhere.
- Up

1445
02:28:48,078 --> 02:28:53,106
Darned luck. No one ever caught us
when we were in the thick of it

1446
02:28:54,117 --> 02:28:59,680
But the moment we quit...
- Why did you get into all this ?

1447
02:29:03,660 --> 02:29:10,828
l wanted to become someone important.
- And... you became ?

1448
02:29:13,070 --> 02:29:15,868
You won't understand.
- Why...

1449
02:29:17,140 --> 02:29:18,402
why won't l understand ?

1450
02:29:19,976 --> 02:29:21,876
Because he never did.
- Who ?

1451
02:29:23,747 --> 02:29:24,714
My father

1452
02:29:28,185 --> 02:29:29,482
He's just like you

1453
02:29:33,190 --> 02:29:34,885
You're trying to con me again

1454
02:29:42,933 --> 02:29:45,902
May l...?
- A smoke ? Sure...

1455
02:29:48,538 --> 02:29:49,470
Where are you going ?

1456
02:29:50,841 --> 02:29:52,638
lf she sees me smoking
she'll scream

1457
02:29:57,781 --> 02:29:59,578
The child will stay with the mother

1458
02:30:08,725 --> 02:30:10,317
What's the use of crying now ?

1459
02:30:12,195 --> 02:30:15,096
Should've considered this beforehand.
- What else to do ?

1460
02:30:17,968 --> 02:30:20,732
Become a ticket collector and
collect ten rupee bribes all my life ?

1461
02:30:29,813 --> 02:30:30,939
You can come in

1462
02:30:49,166 --> 02:30:51,464
We'll have to make a phone call
to your home or mine

1463
02:30:52,068 --> 02:30:56,471
We certainly can't take him with us.
- No, it won't come to that

1464
02:30:56,940 --> 02:31:00,569
l'll figure something.
- And con ourselves out of this one too ?

1465
02:31:00,777 --> 02:31:02,176
What else to do ?

1466
02:31:04,080 --> 02:31:08,107
Take with me to jail, the very son
for whose sake l gave up everything ?

1467
02:31:12,856 --> 02:31:17,343
What justice ! Jails are for reforming.
And here, three people are being jailed

1468
02:31:17,344 --> 02:31:21,161
Text: By RahelSurshi :)

1469
02:31:21,364 --> 02:31:24,231
Two of whom have reformed
and a third who's completely innocent

1470
02:31:26,036 --> 02:31:31,668
Don't worry Vimmi. l'll crack a plan.
- What plan Rakesh ?

1471
02:31:32,042 --> 02:31:33,703
We've run out of plans

1472
02:31:40,484 --> 02:31:42,679
Vimmi do you have any idea
what jails are like ?

1473
02:31:48,558 --> 02:31:50,458
How will you spend
so many years inside one ?

1474
02:31:54,664 --> 02:31:59,966
Let's do something,
l'll take the blame for everything

1475
02:32:02,239 --> 02:32:05,538
Then you're free to go home
to Fursatganj with the baby

1476
02:32:08,678 --> 02:32:10,873
All you wanted was to become a model

1477
02:32:13,250 --> 02:32:14,808
l dragged you into this whole thing

1478
02:32:21,057 --> 02:32:26,359
You can't even make a cup of tea
for yourself. ln jail... how ?

1479
02:32:26,530 --> 02:32:30,296
l'll manage Vimmi,
don't worry about me

1480
02:32:32,636 --> 02:32:34,695
Have you ever managed to do
anything alone ?

1481
02:32:34,971 --> 02:32:43,401
ln any case,
Bunty is nothing without Babli

1482
02:33:05,635 --> 02:33:06,567
Get up

1483
02:33:07,571 --> 02:33:08,435
Unlock yourselves...

1484
02:33:10,140 --> 02:33:11,038
l can't do it...

1485
02:33:12,976 --> 02:33:14,603
We're nearing the railway signal
on the outskirts of Delhi

1486
02:33:17,047 --> 02:33:18,605
The train halts there for two minutes

1487
02:33:20,750 --> 02:33:21,774
The two of...

1488
02:33:23,019 --> 02:33:27,319
The three of you can get off
and go wherever you wish

1489
02:33:28,692 --> 02:33:31,320
No one recognises
Bunty and Babli except me

1490
02:33:34,164 --> 02:33:35,529
And no one ever will

1491
02:33:55,051 --> 02:33:58,145
Sir...
- Shut up. Not a word

1492
02:33:59,022 --> 02:34:01,149
Or l just might change my mind

1493
02:34:02,192 --> 02:34:02,817
Get going

1494
02:34:06,196 --> 02:34:07,663
That's enough

1495
02:34:32,555 --> 02:34:38,221
Whether it was my life's biggest mistake
or their best con act, l didn't know

1496
02:34:40,397 --> 02:34:43,924
But policemen are human too,
believe it or not...

1497
02:34:45,135 --> 02:34:49,037
we wear those uniforms only on our body,
at heart we're as vulnerable as babies

1498
02:34:51,775 --> 02:34:57,873
l believed l had destroyed Bunty-Babli,
so l let Rakesh and Vimmi go...

1499
02:34:58,948 --> 02:35:06,320
because l think the law needs
to destroy crime, not lives

1500
02:35:07,657 --> 02:35:10,558
The bank's gold was recovered from
the spot Babli had indicated

1501
02:35:11,628 --> 02:35:18,557
The recoveries continued
for months afterwards...

1502
02:35:19,035 --> 02:35:22,061
Monies and valuables
stolen by Bunty and Babli

1503
02:35:22,272 --> 02:35:25,571
l think they had told me
the truth about going back...

1504
02:35:25,809 --> 02:35:29,802
to live respectable,
honest lives like their parents

1505
02:35:37,754 --> 02:35:40,587
Rakesh'ji could you perhaps
increase the pressure

1506
02:35:45,628 --> 02:35:46,424
What a joy

1507
02:35:50,467 --> 02:35:54,460
This world we live in
has two kinds of Pappus. One...

1508
02:35:55,004 --> 02:35:57,438
the kind who obey their parents
and get to eat chocolates

1509
02:35:57,841 --> 02:36:01,937
and the kind that doesn't
and gets locked up inside toilets

1510
02:36:02,145 --> 02:36:03,635
You are...?
- The first

1511
02:36:05,148 --> 02:36:06,615
My darling baby

1512
02:36:07,984 --> 02:36:11,442
But he didn't even drink his milk.
- He'll eat the chocolate

1513
02:36:12,322 --> 02:36:14,813
What good are chocolates?
You and your fads

1514
02:36:15,024 --> 02:36:19,393
No, l'm feeling cold...
- Forget the cold. Be fashionable

1515
02:36:25,401 --> 02:36:26,834
What are you teaching Pappu ?

1516
02:36:27,504 --> 02:36:31,964
To speak the truth
and pray every morning

1517
02:36:32,175 --> 02:36:35,542
Where's my son ? One of his friends
is waiting downstairs

1518
02:36:36,679 --> 02:36:39,876
Friends and folks in Fursatganj
find all the time for fun

1519
02:36:40,083 --> 02:36:43,678
You fix the name of this city.
l'll fix this friend

1520
02:36:47,924 --> 02:36:50,654
My son is genius from...

1521
02:36:51,661 --> 02:36:52,650
childhood

1522
02:36:53,663 --> 02:36:55,221
l am very lucky

1523
02:36:55,565 --> 02:36:58,659
l got a daughter-in-law
who is very very smart

1524
02:37:00,036 --> 02:37:03,096
lt's such a joy to know that
our son and his wife...

1525
02:37:03,306 --> 02:37:08,073
have done things so important that
your department still remembers them

1526
02:37:10,013 --> 02:37:15,815
Never told folks at home
what all you achieved ?

1527
02:37:16,553 --> 02:37:19,044
Maybe you should tell us

1528
02:37:21,558 --> 02:37:23,185
Nervous already ?

1529
02:37:25,562 --> 02:37:27,052
A scam is in the offing

1530
02:37:29,232 --> 02:37:30,494
Huge scam

1531
02:37:33,703 --> 02:37:34,670
Sir...

1532
02:37:37,006 --> 02:37:40,737
l swear by my son,
l've given it up

1533
02:37:42,245 --> 02:37:44,440
l've no idea of
what scams are happening

1534
02:37:45,982 --> 02:37:48,382
For three years now,
l'm following a work-home-work routine

1535
02:37:48,585 --> 02:37:51,782
This scam has got to be stopped.
- Then go ahead and stop it

1536
02:37:57,927 --> 02:37:59,121
We cannot stop it

1537
02:38:00,530 --> 02:38:01,929
Who else can ?

1538
02:38:05,702 --> 02:38:06,498
You

1539
02:38:11,674 --> 02:38:15,804
Then save me from this
respectable-dignified life ! Please

1540
02:38:16,145 --> 02:38:17,976
Who's saying this ?
You or...?
- We both

1541
02:38:19,949 --> 02:38:20,973
l'm through

1542
02:38:21,217 --> 02:38:24,744
lf l make mango pickle
one more time l'll die

1543
02:38:24,954 --> 02:38:26,581
lt's killing me, Rakesh

1544
02:38:45,141 --> 02:38:48,633
Keep the faith

1545
02:39:19,842 --> 02:39:22,675
Hace tiempo me dijo que estaba
en el negocio de la limpieza

1546
02:39:22,879 --> 02:39:25,814
Once upon a time he told me that
he was in the business of cleaning

1547
02:39:28,254 --> 02:40:00,146
Text By RahelSurshi =)
